Generic single-database configuration with an async dbapi.

Alembic will:
- Load the Alembic configuration from alembic.ini
- Load the alembic/env.py file, which provides the
  run_migrations_offline() and run_migrations_online() functions
- Discover migration files from the alembic/versions directory
- Compare the database schema with the target_metadata in env.py
- Generate migration scripts automatically

